{"tid":405314,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"王嘉儀新歌《美麗新世界》","createTime":"2017-09-18T17:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T17:44:31.000Z","uid":4260,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2615b7d46621a700576e8e355eba7ca597e704f8","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/015620_d10329073c8a77990edf8f5babb17cc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F015620_d10329073c8a77990edf8f5babb17cc0.jpg&h=e59cfca3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時代急速，世界越變越快越壞越陌生；<br />\n科技進步，辨不出真偽也分不出善惡；<br />\n分辨是否必要，真相是否必要；<br />\n是你瘋了，還是我瘋了。<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n科幻不再科幻 ， 未來瞬即變成當下。<br />\n美麗新世界。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCredit後補<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kp5vBA1JX48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fkp5vBA1JX48&d=opQEqxIgtScb8AYB8yliN%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e76612d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kp5vBA1JX48</a>"},{"pid":"dcea920cf97599981990171ffe0bb68c74be1689","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1817a67b6f34b5aebbede65f8d97d49d20f3c8","tid":405314,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adaee96eb55cb040a0f476d4565043601d34a275","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b0bfa93c2f8fad791bd973fa842aa5d74dabcd","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4353dde98f190434f98f549c953bda42c7161f02","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f9edab4940e68366c02c296c995d5b67f1e5b0","tid":405314,"uid":104499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"我鍾意佢搵Nick tong夾個隻 夕陽無限好  btw幾鍾意佢 如果隻出碟係jazz tone就正 <br />\n佢把聲好夾jazz底"},{"pid":"338d301b355a65e4a8a959f61d87dce8803ce4c6","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b20e04674e4267d4d9f661985c9d41381113775","tid":405314,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1342eafcf3d7cf601169be799f16443315630df4","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bb4ffd306906d31df65a654f4673e77a8b224a","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T18:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a2ac3398651afedffc05d42028542acf54a6d4","tid":405314,"uid":23275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:43:14.000Z","msg":"好正阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c239312f4426813a0a8cc40f29137899ecaac324","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T06:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588bf588c97a4e1384c3f1769fa22729742375a1","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"作詞: 王樂儀 作曲: 王嘉儀 <br />\n編曲: 黃少雍 監製: 王嘉儀<br />\n<br />\n煙花燒一晚<br />\n街燈眨一下<br />\n光輝的都市 完美吧<br />\n誰 張開口想喊<br />\n卻剎那變啞<br />\n世界要慶祝 無烏鴉<br />\n<br />\n站到街邊 靜了一點<br />\n下載一首 冷的詩<br />\n螢幕有光 亂轉畫面<br />\n略過身邊 動踂已幻滅<br />\n<br />\n誰變了瘋子<br />\n若為世界哽咽<br />\n要避免露面<br />\n但大進化優先<br />\n從此悲傷只准按鍵<br />\n愉快靠指尖 （碰著發現）<br />\n<br />\n不進則退擺脫到嗎<br />\n只要適應不會眼花<br />\n好過一世看頹垣敗瓦<br />\n虛構飛鳥不會太假<br />\n轉眼輸送一抹尾巴<br />\n一剎一世已成為習慣<br />\n<br />\n坐到窗邊 悶了一點<br />\n沒有找到 半張紙<br />\n時代太急 就以晶片<br />\n代替枯枝 換去了春天<br />\n<br />\n誰變了瘋子<br />\n若為世界哽咽<br />\n要避免露面<br />\n但大進化優先<br />\n從此悲傷只准按鍵<br />\n愉快靠指尖 （碰著有電）<br />\n<br />\n不進則退擺脫到嗎<br />\n鑲嵌的眼走馬看花<br />\n光纖碰不到有靈魂在喊<br />\n虛構飛鳥不會太假<br />\n精緻的臉不會太假<br />\n可惜我瘋了我靈魂在喊<br />\n<br />\n誰太過瘋癲<br />\n站在世界之巔<br />\n揭露惡或善<br />\n忘記進化優先<br />\n留低觸感肌膚發熱<br />\n誰碰我指尖<br />\n(不進則退擺脫到嗎<br />\n鑲嵌的眼走馬看花<br />\n光纖碰不到有靈魂在喊)<br />\n(虛構飛鳥不會太假<br />\n精緻的臉不會太假<br />\n可惜我瘋了我靈魂在喊)"},{"pid":"d5d963796519744507bad5ba17c0b3c1949d0ef2","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"各大音樂平台已逐漸上架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69081fef1e313ed4cd89871e0f849c47d340562","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T19:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cd842e32f4039d692589c5317a70f192253032","tid":405314,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2f73b96edb9557b3f84b4362abc002904c33e1","tid":405314,"uid":35368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"唔錯"},{"pid":"94d6e429e632fbbf12a818ad72968eb226bfde42","tid":405314,"uid":129443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我鍾意佢搵Nick tong夾個隻 夕陽無限好  btw幾鍾意佢 如果隻出碟係jazz tone